      <scopecontent id="aspace_368bffb339963cd398479b6bd78485ac">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Forty-eight letters between Lluís Baró Segimón and his wife, Pilar Val de Baró. Lluís Baró Segimón fought with the Republican 27th Division during the Spanish Civil War, and postmarks indicate that Lluís wrote from the front lines of the war to Pilar in Morell, Tarragona.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
